4b01d338-ed15-4ae0-8555-c907614f71c7.title: <player>
4b01d338-ed15-4ae0-8555-c907614f71c7.text:
Captain Lawgof sent me. He's having trouble with his
cannon.

6cec3f15-2345-495b-acd6-4749dd1a7067.title: Nulodion
6cec3f15-2345-495b-acd6-4749dd1a7067.text: Of course, we forgot to send the ammo mould!

8335e3e0-46b5-4fa9-a361-d7e872b32b50.title: Nulodion
8335e3e0-46b5-4fa9-a361-d7e872b32b50.text:
Don't be silly - the ammo's made by using a mould.
Here, take these to him. The instructions explain
everything.

f20b240f-b5f4-4c4f-8c51-3b120eae8ce4.title: Nulodion
f20b240f-b5f4-4c4f-8c51-3b120eae8ce4.text:
Thank you, adventurer. The Dwarf Black Guard will
remember this.

02724725-5c69-4ece-886b-6d2146db5caf.title: Nulodion
02724725-5c69-4ece-886b-6d2146db5caf.text:
So has the Captain figured out how to work the cannon
yet?

dd569ef5-0664-450b-b06b-806095822a46.title: <player>
dd569ef5-0664-450b-b06b-806095822a46.text: Not yet, but I'm sure he will.

b5315191-97a5-4516-bf82-0dd40c0ad6e8.title: Nulodion
b5315191-97a5-4516-bf82-0dd40c0ad6e8.text: If you can get those items to him it'll be a great help.

4a6aeaa3-7ea9-44b0-8eac-8d789a64b6c1.title: Nulodion
4a6aeaa3-7ea9-44b0-8eac-8d789a64b6c1.text: Deary me, you are trouble. Here, take this one.

641f8819-b7eb-4a6f-a354-0a8037a6c6ab.title: Nulodion
641f8819-b7eb-4a6f-a354-0a8037a6c6ab.text: I'm good, just working hard as usual...

options.text: I was hoping you might sell me a cannon?
Well, take care of yourself then.
I want to know more about the cannon.

47668239-f44f-44e6-96a2-b3cb6ddb4664.title: <player>
47668239-f44f-44e6-96a2-b3cb6ddb4664.text: Well, take care of yourself then.

1b23c06e-d864-450e-9bb3-cf0e6c3e38f2.title: <player>
1b23c06e-d864-450e-9bb3-cf0e6c3e38f2.text: I want to know more about the cannon.

e08f59f2-1995-43cc-b72e-d5bd0224cf20.title: Nulodion
e08f59f2-1995-43cc-b72e-d5bd0224cf20.text:
There's only so much I can tell you, adventurer.
We've been working on this little beauty for some time
now.

264917e9-cd10-46f9-b127-f71492c535d3.title: Nulodion
264917e9-cd10-46f9-b127-f71492c535d3.text:
In short bursts it's very effective, the most destructive
weapon to date. The cannon automatically targets
monsters close by. You just have to make the ammo
and let rip.

99b9bbe6-77f8-4fae-8a0d-48c23de30269.title: Nulodion
99b9bbe6-77f8-4fae-8a0d-48c23de30269.text:
That's unfortunate... but don't worry, I can sort you
out.

6e7aaa1f-301f-4581-8172-e0308cc6f52c.title: Nulodion
6e7aaa1f-301f-4581-8172-e0308cc6f52c.text:
Oh dear, I'm only allowed to replace cannons that were
stolen in action. I'm sorry, but you'll have to buy a
new set.

7b9b8973-3fde-4a42-9d76-aad9b693e66c.title: <player>
7b9b8973-3fde-4a42-9d76-aad9b693e66c.text: I was hoping you might sell me a cannon.

6a731f7f-3dbc-4d58-92a8-cf6df2c0c381.title: Nulodion
6a731f7f-3dbc-4d58-92a8-cf6df2c0c381.text:
I shouldn't really, but as you helped us so much, well, I
could sort something out. I'll warn you though, they
don't come cheap!

8fdb155a-5955-4925-a1f8-d8d3e6cb7b85.title: Nulodion
8fdb155a-5955-4925-a1f8-d8d3e6cb7b85.text:
For the full setup, 750,000 coins. Or I can sell you
the separate parts... but it'll cost extra!

options.text: Okay, I'll take a cannon please.
Can I look at the separate parts please?
Sorry, that's too much for me.
Have you any ammo or instructions to sell?

70f04674-971a-4a50-96aa-e77fecf9c9fa.title: <player>
70f04674-971a-4a50-96aa-e77fecf9c9fa.text: Have you any ammo or instructions to sell?

a8982f90-325e-49b0-bc12-769a359031a9.title: <player>
a8982f90-325e-49b0-bc12-769a359031a9.text: Sorry, that's too much for me.

ae36599f-2628-43da-8a1c-142026a3ca74.title: Nulodion
ae36599f-2628-43da-8a1c-142026a3ca74.text: Fair enough, it's too much for most of us.

6e158d32-2743-4dcb-a2cb-9e07ae2892d2.title: <player>
6e158d32-2743-4dcb-a2cb-9e07ae2892d2.text: Can I look at the separate parts please?

19535339-d73b-4c0d-9b9c-b266504a06a8.title: <player>
19535339-d73b-4c0d-9b9c-b266504a06a8.text: Okay, I'll take a cannon please.

dbe58103-a028-45d7-955f-52ec9194482d.title: Nulodion
dbe58103-a028-45d7-955f-52ec9194482d.text: Okay then, but keep it quiet... This thing's top secret!

7da8fdff-1ccd-4755-92bf-3a42734ef880.title: <player>
7da8fdff-1ccd-4755-92bf-3a42734ef880.text: Oops, I don't have enough money.

0eedf38e-d247-46ca-802e-f8d4d9301df2.title: Nulodion
0eedf38e-d247-46ca-802e-f8d4d9301df2.text: Sorry, I can't go any lower than that.

b02d5809-6ce2-4869-b42d-1a065255db73.title: <player>
b02d5809-6ce2-4869-b42d-1a065255db73.text: Okay, I'll take a cannon please.

95faac9d-8844-4cb6-95b9-67cb0e2ab65f.title: Nulodion
95faac9d-8844-4cb6-95b9-67cb0e2ab65f.text: Okay then, but keep it quiet... This thing's top secret!

1318b616-96e6-4eff-bd03-4b563ae1eec5.text: You give the Cannon engineer 750,000 coins...

297e73d3-1831-4843-a062-42b2656f786c.text:
He gives you the four parts that make the cannon, plus an ammo
mould and an instruction manual.

ae9042df-80f3-40ec-9d97-132f5daee3b0.title: Nulodion
ae9042df-80f3-40ec-9d97-132f5daee3b0.text: There you go, you be careful with that thing.

b8b524d1-1661-4729-ad56-93577dfe8f03.title: Note
b8b524d1-1661-4729-ad56-93577dfe8f03.text: Character stat check for lost cannon
